def scale_dataset(W_num, scaler_type = 'standard'):
    
    if scaler_type == 'standard':
        scaler = StandardScaler()
    
    elif scaler_type == 'minmax':
        scaler = MinMaxScaler()
    
    elif scaler_type == 'robust':
        scaler = RobustScaler()
    
    elif scaler_type == 'maxabs':
        scaler = MaxAbsScaler()
    
    else:
        raise ValueError("Invalid scaler_type. Supported types are 'standard', 'minmax', 'robust', and 'maxabs'.")

    scaled_num = scaler.fit_transform(W_num)
    
    
    scaled_num = pd.DataFrame(scaled_num, columns=W_num.columns) 
        
    return scaled_num
